nodes.text: Beta Ioli was a female Duros Junior Lieutenant in the Galactic Alliance Guard who was a part of the crew of the Anakin Solo.

She was part of the the crew of the Rover, under the command of Jedi apprentice Ben Skywalker, that was sent to Terephon to find out what had become of Jaina Solo and Zekk after their mission to Terephon. She was killed when the Rover was destroyed in the Battle of Hapes.
